<plot>Las Vegas, the last American boomtown, licensed to sell dreams it peddles fantasy and escapism for $6 billion a year. Through the stories of four people this feature length documentary takes the audience behind the garish facade of this extraordinary desert town and reveals how high the stakes are in Sin City.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?239048</url></doc>
